## Development

This project uses the Nebula Protocol for structured development.
See `ROADMAP.md` for the project plan.

## Running Tests

```bash
# Run all tests
pytest

# Run with coverage
pytest --cov=todo

# Run specific test file
pytest tests/test_smoke.py
```

## Code Quality

```bash
# Format code
black src/ tests/

# Lint code
flake8 src/ tests/
```

## Usage

### Installation (Development Mode)

```bash
pip install -e .
```

### Commands

```bash
# Add a todo
todo add "Buy groceries"

# List todos
todo list                # All todos
todo list --active       # Active only
todo list --completed    # Completed only

# Complete a todo (use first 4+ chars of ID shown in list)
todo complete <id>

# Delete a todo
todo delete <id>
```

